{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/정규-표현식/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"정규-표현식이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EA%B7%9C-%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84%EC%8B%9D%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"정규 표현식이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정규 표현식이란</h2>\n<p>텍스트를 찾고 조작하는 데 쓰는 문자열. </p>\n<h2 id=\"문자-하나-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 하나 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 하나 찾기</h2>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"문자-그대로-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EA%B7%B8%EB%8C%80%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 그대로 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 그대로 찾기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, my name is Kim. Nice to meet you. my phone number is 000\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">Kim</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nstr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">match</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">my</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// [ 'my', 'my' ]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"모든-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%A0-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"모든 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>모든 문자 찾기</h3>\n<p>정규 표현식에서는 특별한 문자들(혹은 집합 문자)을 써 무엇을 검색할지 결정한다. <strong>마침표 문자(.)</strong>는 아무 문자 하나와 일치한다. 마침표는 어떠한 문자나 알파벳, 숫자, 심지어 문자 부호로 쓰인 마침표(.) 자체와도 일치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  text1.txt\n  image.png\n  file.txt\n  test.txt\n  image2.jpeg\n  image.jpg\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">.txt</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>마침표를 연속으로 사용하면 어떠한 문자든 붙어있는 마침표 개수만큼 일치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  text1.txt\n  image.png\n  file.txt\n  test.txt\n  image2.jpeg\n  image.jpg\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">....txt</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"특수문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%88%98%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"특수문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특수문자 찾기</h3>\n<p>마침표는 정규 표현식에서 특별한 의미가 있다. 마침표를 찾으려고 한다면 마침표 앞에 역슬래시(\\)를 붙이면 된다. <code class=\"language-text\">\\.</code>은 마침표 자체와 일치한다. 정규 표현식에서는 특수 문자 자체와 일치하는 패턴을 찾을 때 역슬래시를 사용하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">text1.txt</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\.txt</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"문자-집합으로-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%A7%91%ED%95%A9%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 집합으로 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 집합으로 찾기</h2>\n<p>문자 집합을 사용하면 특정 문자들과 문자 범위를 일치시킬 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"여러-문자-중-하나와-일치시키기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%AC%EB%9F%AC-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%A4%91-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98%EC%99%80-%EC%9D%BC%EC%B9%98%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"여러 문자 중 하나와 일치시키기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>여러 문자 중 하나와 일치시키기</h3>\n<p>정규표현식에서는 메타 문자인 대괄호([])를 이용해 문자 집합을 표현한다. 대괄호 안에 있는 문자는 모두 집합의 구성원이 되며, 집합에 속한 문자 가운데 하나가 일치한다. AND가 아닌 OR로 동작.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\nna1.xls\nna2.xls\nsa1.xls\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">[ns]a[0-9].xls</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>A-Z는 A부터 Z사이에 있는 모든 대문자와 일치</li>\n<li>a-z는 a부터 z사이에 있는 모든 소문자와 일치</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n&lt;div color=\"#fff000\" text=\"#333737\" />\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">#[0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f]</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"제외하고-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"제외하고 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>제외하고 찾기</h3>\n<p>캐럿 (^) 문자를 사용해서 제외할 문자 집합을 지정한다. 캐럿 문자는 이 문자 바로 뒤에 있는 문자나 범위뿐만 아니라 집합 안에 있는 문자나 범위를 모두 제외한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\nnam.xls\nna1.xls\nna2.xls\nsa1.xls\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">[ns]a[^0-9].xls</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"메타-문자-사용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A9%94%ED%83%80-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"메타 문자 사용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>메타 문자 사용하기</h2>\n<div class=\"reference__md\">\n[참고]<br/>함수형 자바스크립트, 루이스 아텐시오 저. 한빛미디어\n</div>","timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"…","fields":{"slug":"/posts/정규-표현식/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"정규 표현식","status":"published","description":"정규 표현식에 관한 공부","date":"December 10, 2019","categories":["programming"],"tags":["programming","regular expression"],"template":"posts","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/정규-표현식/","previous":{"id":"0b640361-2981-5fac-ae16-627018d2b94c","frontmatter":{"title":"함수형 자바스크립트","tags":["javascript","programming","functional programming"],"categories":["javascript"],"template":"posts","status":"published"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/함수형-자바스크립트/"}},"next":{"id":"2589903a-4c3d-5c43-af88-487d62b8d7b2","frontmatter":{"title":"정렬 Sorting","tags":["programming","algorithm","sorting"],"categories":["programming"],"template":"posts","status":"published"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/정렬-sorting/"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}